commit.message: Center the map upon droneLocation change
Mapbox is centered at the droneLocation
Can run the app without drone connection

Added Drone movement feature

- Double click to instantly move the drone
- Right click to move the drone with animation (will update the regulations as it goes)

Added Altitude

- Altitude now is displayed in the web app
- Layout has been modified to better show all regulations
- Tooltips have been fixed (N/A and direction)

Added Battery Regulation

- Battery Percent now shows up on web app
- Skirball theater is now set as the starting location
- FA icons are used for the battery percent

Patrially updated for Bebop 3.2.0

- Added HAS_JOYSTICK toggle
- Using custom master build of cylon-bebop to depend on node-bebop 0.5.0
Added right-click to move drone feature
Added hover boxes to map to show what each layer is
